        en: "Nanoseconds since UNIX epoch, captured by the publisher at write time.",
        fr: "Nanosecondes depuis l'epoch UNIX, capturé par le publisher au moment du write.",
      },
    },
    {
      offset: 24, length: 4, name: "text.length", type: "u32",
      value: "10",
      note: {
        en: "String length INCLUDING the mandatory null terminator. \"hello #13\" is 9 chars + 1 = 10.",
        fr: "Longueur de la string INCLUANT le null terminator obligatoire. \"hello #13\" fait 9 chars + 1 = 10.",
      },
    },
    {
      offset: 28, length: 9, name: "text content", type: "char[9]",
      value: "\"hello #13\"",
      note: {
        en: "UTF-8 bytes of the string content, no length prefix here — that came right before.",
        fr: "Bytes UTF-8 du contenu de la string, pas de préfixe de longueur ici — il vient juste avant.",
      },
    },
    {
      offset: 37, length: 1, name: "text null", type: "char",
      value: "\\0",
      note: {
        en: "CDR strings always end with a null byte. Counted in text.length.",
        fr: "Les strings CDR finissent toujours par un byte null. Compté dans text.length.",
      },
